<li><a href="http://www.philosophytalk.org/pastShows/AnimalRights.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.philosophytalk.org/pastShows/AnimalRights.htm" rel="nofollow">Radio Discussion of Animal Rights with Activist and Philosopher Lori Gruen</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.vorlesungen-tierrechte.de/media/index.php?v=regan" class="external text" title="http://www.vorlesungen-tierrechte.de/media/index.php?v=regan" rel="nofollow">Video of Tom Regan's lecture "Animal Rights: An Introduction." at the Interdisciplinary Lectures on Animal Rights at the Ruprecht-Karls-University Heidelberg on the 24th of May 2006</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.nabranimallaw.org" class="external text" title="http://www.nabranimallaw.org" rel="nofollow">The National Association for Biomedical Research Animal Law Section</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.animal-law.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.animal-law.org/" rel="nofollow">Animal Law Project</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.lclark.edu/org/animalaw/" class="external text" title="http://www.lclark.edu/org/animalaw/" rel="nofollow"><i>Animal Law Review</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.aldf.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.aldf.org/" rel="nofollow">Animal Legal Defense Fund (ALDF)</a>.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cala-online.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.cala-online.org/" rel="nofollow">The Center on Animal Liberation Affairs (CALA)</a></li>
