og attack">Dog attack</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Dog_fighting" title="Dog fighting">Dog fighting</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Dog_licence" title="Dog licence">Dog licence</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Dog_tag" title="Dog tag">Dog tag</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ethology" title="Ethology">Ethology</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Emotion_in_animals" title="Emotion in animals">Emotion in animals</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Factory_farming" title="Factory farming">Factory farming</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Feral" title="Feral">Feral</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Human_bonding" title="Human bonding">Human-animal bond</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Neutering" title="Neutering">Neutering</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/No-kill_shelter" title="No-kill shelter">No-kill shelter</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Pet" title="Pet">Pet</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Pet_adoption" title="Pet adoption">Pet adoption</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Pet_cemetery" title="Pet cemetery">Pet cemetery</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Pet_food" title="Pet food">Pet food</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Pet_insurance" title="Pet insurance">Pet insurance</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Rainbow_Bridge_(pets)" title="Rainbow Bridge (pets)">Rainbow Bridge</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Rescue_group" title="Rescue group">Rescue group</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Society_for_the_Preventio